title: Einolf, Faurote make spring Dean's List
title_page: Mount St. Mary's: Einolf, Faurote make spring Dean's List
maintext: Nicholas Einolf of Fort Wayne and Vincent Faurote of Decatur have been named to the spring Dean’s List at Mount St. Mary’s University, the Emmitsburg, Maryland-based university has announced.
